{"seo": [], "title": "LAWRENCE KIMATHI KIAMBI", "parent": null, "cta_link": "entry::1552", "cta_text": "Back to Members", "leadership": "board-of-director", "updated_by": 2, "footer_type": "footers/main_footer", "header_type": "headers/country", "bottom_bar_nav": null, "team_member_text": "<p>Lawrence Kimathi holds a Masters in Business Administration (MBA) with a merit from Warwick Business School UK, a Bachelor of Science degree majoring in accounting from United States International University – Africa (USIU) and is a Certified Public Accountant of Kenya, CPA (K). He is a member of the Institute of Certified Public Accountants of Kenya and Institute of Directors. His senior leadership experience spans over 25 years having worked as Finance Director/CFO in a number of multinational organizations which include Cadbury East and Central Africa, AIG, East Africa Breweries Limited, BAT Sub Sahara Africa and BAT PLC in London.</p>
<br>

<p>OTHER DIRECTORSHIPS: Lawrence serves in the KCB Uganda board and is a trustee of the KCB Staff Pension Fund defined benefit scheme.</p>", "designation_title": "Designation", "member_text_title": "Education and Professional Background:", "team_member_image": "uganda/team/Lawrence-Kiambi.jpg", "appointment_date_title": "Appointment Date", "member_appointment_date": null, "team_member_designation": "Director"}

{"seo": [], "title": "RAMLA NANTONGO MUNYAKAZI", "parent": null, "cta_link": null, "cta_text": "Back to Members", "leadership": "executive-management", "updated_by": 2, "footer_type": "footers/main_footer", "header_type": "headers/country", "bottom_bar_nav": null, "team_member_text": "<h3>Education and Professional Background:</h3>
               <span>Ramla holds an MBA from Edinburgh Business School- Herriot Watt University and a bachelor’s degree in International Business from United States International University -Nairobi.

Ramla is a seasoned Banker with significant industry wide experience in corporate and SME business development, having worked in financial services for over 13 years. She also has vast experience in strategy formulation and implementation, relationship management, credit risk management and structured financing, among others.</span>", "designation_title": "Designation", "member_text_title": "Education and Professional Background:", "team_member_image": "uganda/team/ramal.jpg", "appointment_date_title": "Appointment Date", "member_appointment_date": null, "team_member_designation": "Head of Corporate Banking"}

{"seo": [], "title": "NYANGWESO VINCENT", "parent": null, "cta_link": null, "cta_text": "Back to Members", "leadership": "executive-management", "updated_by": 2, "footer_type": "footers/main_footer", "header_type": "headers/country", "bottom_bar_nav": null, "team_member_text": "<h3>Education and Professional Background:</h3>
               <span>Vincent has over 17 years’ experience in banking. Prior to his appointment as Head of Operations he served in different capacities in KCB as Manager shared services and Operational Excellence, and Manager Branch Support. He has also previously worked with Bank of Africa as Customer care Supervisor, Branch operations Manager, Operations risk manager, Branch Manager.

Vincent holds a master’s degree in finance and Accounting and Bachelor of Science degree in Quantitative Economics. He also done several Leadership trainings.</span>", "designation_title": "Designation", "member_text_title": "Education and Professional Background:", "team_member_image": "uganda/team/nyangweso-vincent.jpg", "appointment_date_title": "Appointment Date", "member_appointment_date": null, "team_member_designation": "Head of operations"}
